00:50:56,356 --> 00:50:57,983
<b>I realized that too late.</b>

529
00:51:03,447 --> 00:51:04,531
<b>I wanted to tell</b>

530
00:51:07,367 --> 00:51:09,244
<b>my mom that I don't</b>

