00:51:12,831 --> 00:51:14,040
<b>resent her.</b>

532
00:51:14,708 --> 00:51:16,835
<b>THE PATIENT SEEMS TO WANT
TO RESOLVE HIS ISSUES WITH HIS PARENTS</b>

533
00:51:19,880 --> 00:51:20,881
<b>Ma'am.</b>

534
00:51:22,966 --> 00:51:25,218
<b>The patient didn't resent
any of his family.</b>

535
00:51:26,011 --> 00:51:27,679
<b>It was quite the opposite.</b>

536
00:51:36,855 --> 00:51:38,023
<b>Really?</b>

537
00:51:40,358 --> 00:51:41,276
<b>I see.</b>

538
00:51:48,950 --> 00:51:50,076
<b>I'm sorry, Mom.</b>

