545
00:52:54,599 --> 00:52:57,978
<b>Right. We've been living
in this house for over 20 years.</b>

546
00:52:58,645 --> 00:53:02,023
<b>After you passed away,
Mom brought all of your stuff</b>

547
00:53:02,107 --> 00:53:04,234
<b>from Gang-hwa's house to this room.</b>

548
00:53:04,317 --> 00:53:05,443
<b>Right.</b>

549
00:53:06,111 --> 00:53:08,530
<b>Yu-ri, why don't you start
making glass art again?</b>

