00:54:42,415 --> 00:54:44,250
<b>This isn't like him.</b>

569
00:55:03,853 --> 00:55:05,397
<b>Where are we going?</b>

570
00:55:05,563 --> 00:55:06,564
<b>What?</b>

571
00:55:09,859 --> 00:55:10,902
<b>I'm not sure.</b>

572
00:55:11,861 --> 00:55:15,031
<b>Seo-woo, where should we go?
Where do you want to go?</b>

573
00:55:15,115 --> 00:55:16,658
<b>An amusement park.</b>

574
00:55:23,456 --> 00:55:26,835
<b>Welcome. Please show me
your ticket. Have a great day.</b>

