00:55:27,502 --> 00:55:29,546
<b>Please show me your ticket. Have fun.</b>

576
00:55:29,629 --> 00:55:31,381
<b>Let's say hello to the bear.</b>

577
00:55:32,507 --> 00:55:33,383
<b>Hi.</b>

578
00:55:33,466 --> 00:55:35,677
<b>-My gosh, you look like a princess.
-A princess?</b>

