584
00:57:11,397 --> 00:57:12,440
<b>Right.</b>

585
00:57:22,826 --> 00:57:24,119
<b>Thank you.</b>

586
00:57:25,036 --> 00:57:27,205
<b>-Seo-woo, say goodbye.
-Goodbye.</b>

587
00:57:34,129 --> 00:57:35,880
<b>She must've been tired to be outside.</b>

588
00:57:36,422 --> 00:57:37,382
<b>Right.</b>

589
00:57:40,969 --> 00:57:42,137
<b>She's so cute.</b>

590
00:57:43,471 --> 00:57:44,556
<b>You know what?</b>

591
00:57:45,181 --> 00:57:48,560
<b>She wriggles her mouth from time to time
while she sleeps.</b>

592
00:57:51,771 --> 00:57:52,939
<b>That's you.</b>

593
00:57:54,065 --> 00:57:55,900
<b>You wriggle your mouth when you sleep.</b>

594
00:57:59,863 --> 00:58:00,905
<b>You're right.</b>

595
00:58:04,826 --> 00:58:06,077
<b>That was my habit.</b>

596
00:58:07,704 --> 00:58:08,830
<b>It was times like these</b>

597
00:58:10,331 --> 00:58:11,541
<b>when I'd be</b>

598
00:58:12,917 --> 00:58:14,377
<b>reminded of you</b>

599
00:58:15,253 --> 00:58:16,713
<b>through Seo-woo.</b>

600
00:58:18,548 --> 00:58:20,800
<b>I began to see bits of you</b>

601
00:58:21,718 --> 00:58:23,678
<b>as Seo-woo grew up little by little.</b>

602
00:58:26,222 --> 00:58:27,849
<b>It's not that I held onto you.</b>

603
00:58:28,850 --> 00:58:30,852
<b>I couldn't help but hold onto you</b>

604
00:58:32,604 --> 00:58:34,564
<b>because you left me with something so big.</b>

605
00:58:40,361 --> 00:58:41,571
<b>But even if</b>

606
00:58:42,655 --> 00:58:44,240
<b>I went back in time,</b>

607
00:58:45,408 --> 00:58:47,035
<b>I still would have saved her.</b>

608
00:59:47,095 --> 00:59:48,638
<b>You know who I am, don't you?</b>

609
00:59:57,647 --> 01:00:00,275
<b>I guess you knew instinctively.</b>

610
01:00:02,068 --> 01:00:05,405
<b>It's not easy to hide one's heart.</b>

611
01:00:23,172 --> 01:00:24,632
<b>I knew it.</b>

612
01:00:26,884 --> 01:00:28,970
<b>I thought it was odd. It happened.</b>

613
01:00:30,388 --> 01:00:31,973
<b>I guess he told you.</b>

614
01:00:38,396 --> 01:00:39,314
<b>Seo-woo's mom.</b>

615
01:00:49,115 --> 01:00:51,784
<b>Why are you surprised?
