616
01:01:01,210 --> 01:01:04,547
<b>Just as you know Seo-woo the best,</b>

617
01:01:05,840 --> 01:01:09,010
<b>I know my daughter the best too.</b>

618
01:01:10,219 --> 01:01:12,722
<b>So I can tell you this for sure.</b>

