01:04:14,028 --> 01:04:15,029
<b>What's going on?</b>

636
01:04:15,112 --> 01:04:16,280
<b>It's Yu-ri.</b>

637
01:04:17,198 --> 01:04:19,825
<b>She's determined to find out
why Yu-ri was the only one</b>

638
01:04:20,409 --> 01:04:22,411
<b>who was sent back here.</b>

639
01:04:43,724 --> 01:04:44,642
<b>Yu-ri.</b>

640
01:04:46,060 --> 01:04:49,230
<b>You should quit
working at the kindergarten too.</b>

641
01:04:50,982 --> 01:04:53,442
