666
01:06:30,915 --> 01:06:31,874
<b><i>I want to live.</i></b>

667
01:06:32,208 --> 01:06:34,043
<b>I want to live, Ms. Mi-dong.</b>

668
01:06:46,847 --> 01:06:49,141
<b>I was wondering
why you didn't spill out your heart yet.</b>

669
01:06:51,435 --> 01:06:52,603
<b>You held out for a long time.</b>

670
01:06:57,692 --> 01:06:59,902
<b>Live. You can live.</b>

671
01:07:02,029 --> 01:07:03,823
<b>But if you don't go back up,</b>

672
01:07:05,116 --> 01:07:09,245
<b>I can't keep my promise that
